               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17950416-82-cd470" type="crimeDate">15th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950416-82-off469 t17950416-82-cd470"></join>, two pewter pint pots, value 1s. 6d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t17950416-82-victim904" type="victimName">
                  Samuel 
                  Phipps
               <interp inst="t17950416-82-victim904" type="surname" value="Phipps"></interp>
